43
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,797
<i>I didn't want to be found,</i>

44
00:02:52,381 --> 00:02:55,008
<i>and I wanted them to find me.</i>

45
00:02:55,008 --> 00:02:58,220
<i>They seem like
polar opposite feelings,</i>

46
00:03:02,307 --> 00:03:06,687
<i>but what I truly hoped for
was just one thing.</i>

47
00:03:08,355 --> 00:03:11,483
Hey, I've been looking for you forever.

48
