Never mind. Let's go.

51
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:29,251
- Ah!

52
00:03:30,627 --> 00:03:32,629
Hey, I think there is

53
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:35,090
a really big dog in there.

54
