This won't do.

56
00:03:54,234 --> 00:03:55,944
- Let's run!

57
00:03:55,944 --> 00:03:57,404
Come on!

58
00:04:10,959 --> 00:04:13,545
<i>I wanted to know
that we were still</i>

59
00:04:15,339 --> 00:04:16,840
<i>good friends,</i>

60
00:04:17,799 --> 00:04:19,843
<i>even though we couldn't talk</i>

61
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:22,721
<i>like we used to.</i>

62
00:05:05,222 --> 00:05:08,559
<i>I wonder what I want right now.</i>

63
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:24,074
<i>I want to distance myself from her.</i>

64
00:05:26,618 --> 00:05:29,454
<i>But I also want to get closer to her.</i>

65
00:05:30,706 --> 00:05:34,042
<i>These two may seem
like polar opposite feelings.</i>

66
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:40,757
Do you want to go to see the sea?

67
00:05:41,508 --> 00:05:42,634
<i>What's certain is</i>

68
00:05:43,343 --> 00:05:47,014
<i>that these countless things
I'm trying to figure out</i>

69
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:53,729
<i>are all about this one person.</i>

70
